Source originally downloaded from 'http://koji.hep.caltech.edu/public/packages/blahp/1.18.0.4/3/src/blahp-1.18.0.4-3.src.rpm'

We are using the following fork - 

https://github.com/brianhlin/BLAH

Particularly the v1_18_bosco branch and we're building the tarball with:

git archive <version tag> | gzip -9 > blahp-<version>.tar.gz

Example:

git archive v1.18.14.bosco | gzip -9 > blahp-1.18.14.bosco.tar.gz